summary: Top 10 Unused Pokémon from the Pokémon Gold Demo
title: Top 10 Unused Pokémon from the Pokémon Gold Demo
body:
If you are a Pokémon fan, you likely already have heard of the recently revealed, unused Pokémon that were attached to the Pokémon Gold Demo. I have seen some AMAZING artwork on tumblr of these Pokémon, and so, with the permission of the artists, here are my Top 10 Unused Pokémon from the Pokémon Gold Demo. HERE WE GO!

#10/#9 - Bell Kitten Pokémon (Evolution Family)

Art Credit: http://blynxee.tumblr.com/ 

#8 - Anchor Shark Pokémon

Art Credit: http://fulmine-art.tumblr.com/

#7 - Twin Ghost Pokémon 

Art Credit: http://ghost-wants-murder.tumblr.com/

#6 - Two-Face Flying Pokémon

Art Credit: http://nekozneko.tumblr.com/

#5 - Missing Shellder Evolution / Slowbro Tail Shell Pokémon / Slowking Crown Shell Pokémon

Art Credit: http://torkart.tumblr.com/

#4/#3 - Polar Wolf Coat Pokémon (Evo. Family)

Art Credit: http://snaptrap-snapsback.tumblr.com/

#2/#1 - Round Electric Tiger Pokémon (Evo. Family)

Art Credit: http://julymarte.tumblr.com/

HONORABLE MENTIONS: 

What do you all think of the Pokémon featured the Pokémon Gold Demo? We have Pokémon Let’s Go Pikachu and Pokémon Let’s Go Eevee coming out next winter for Nintendo Switch! Would you like to see any of these Pokémon make their official debut??
